file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Basic Callbacks
  version: '0.1'
paths:
  "/test":
    get:
      summary: this is a test
      operationId: test
      callbacks:
        expressionWithStaticText:
          http://notificationServer.com?transactionId={$request.body#/id}&email={$request.body}:
            post:
              requestBody:
                content:
                  application/json:
                    schema:
                      type: string
              responses:
                '200':
                  description: webhook successfully processed and no retries will
                    be performed
        expressionWithCurlyBraces:
          "{*}":
            post:
              requestBody:
                content:
                  application/json:
                    schema:
                      type: number
              responses:
                '200':
                  description: webhook 2 successfully processed and no retries will
                    be performed
        onlyExpression:
          "$request.body#/callbackUrl":
            post:
              requestBody:
                content:
                  application/json:
                    schema:
                      type: number
              responses:
                '200':
                  description: webhook 2 successfully processed and no retries will
                    be performed
        invalidExpression:
          "{$request.payload.name}":
            post:
              requestBody:
                content:
                  application/json:
                    schema:
                      type: number
              responses:
                '200':
                  description: webhook 2 successfully processed and no retries will
                    be performed
